Package: cdwtools
Title: Clinical Data Warehouses Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person('Boris', 'Delange', email = 'boris.delange@gmail.com', role = c('cre', 'aut'))
Description: CDW Tools package gives some tools to help clinicians without advanced programmation skills, 
  statisticiants and data scientists use their clinical data warehouse, from patient-level data visualization 
  to pooled patient data analytics, using a web application created with {shiny}.
